"AL amyloidosis = immunoglobulin light-chain amyloidosis; FLC = free light chain; MGUS = monoclonal gammopathy of undetermined significance; MM = multiple myeloma; POEMS = polyneuropathy, organomegaly, endocrinopathy, M protein, and skin changes; PTH = parathyroid hormone; RTA = renal tubular acidosis; VEGF = vascular endothelial growth factor; WM = Waldenström macroglobulinemia."
],
[
{
